oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Tennessee Education Association Building Under Construction, 1961
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the Tennessee Education Association building, located at 602 James Robertson Parkway, under construction, 8 November 1961. The area was part of the Captiol Hill Redevelopment Project (Parcel "F"). Photographed by the Nashville Housing Authority. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
